{"tid":1603530,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎傾下10月1號嘅戰略","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T04:45:12.000Z","uid":33540,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f95c8c13ed8c2d14385b1f71436140739f76d3","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"今日又有好多手捉俾人拉左<br />\n<br />\n我想講下防線嗰問題<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔知點解整個遮陣就當係防線<br />\n<br />\n的確遮係可以當子彈<br />\n<br />\n但係當啲畜龍衝嗰時就冇野擋到<br />\n<br />\n雖然宜家鐵馬買少見少<br />\n<br />\n但係如果見到有都整返個三角鐵馬<br />\n<br />\n第一 當畜龍衝埋黎嗰時 有個緩衝區俾前線 冇咁大壓迫咁死守係防線<br />\n<br />\n第二 進攻 唔知記唔記得612 三角鐵馬係用黎撞長盾狗<br />\n<br />\n如果係進攻 可以配合陣式 <br />\n<br />\n例如一個三角鐵馬 由4-5個人推 一排封滿行車線<br />\n<br />\n第二排幾遮陣掩護<br />\n<br />\n第三排長竹鐵枝近攻<br />\n<br />\n打後用磚 等頭排到狗防線 換火攻<br />\n<br />\n如果有水馬仲好 可以輕少少<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得612係前線近攻打得幾好 輸係輸嗰時冇gear 輸俾tg<br />\n<br />\n但係宜家齊裝返宜近攻好似倒退左<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論戰術方案<br />\n<br />\n祝大家武運亨昌<br />\n<br />\n10月1賀佢老母<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f53234f0bf076af5e97ae37cdb712634ab36efb6","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:54:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR: 應該整返啲實在啲嘅防線宜唔係遮陣or擺幾個鐵馬係路到叫防線</span></span>"},{"pid":"26f5baca237cfae010bc249dfe1c64a09872dcd5","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"利申 冷氣軍司"},{"pid":"8554317ac034bde74bb4429188011290dcedf23b","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c7e46abc859ec0e2a6ed69f3a250a270009fcbf2","tid":1603530,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"（文宣 賀佢老母）10.1準備左好多中國國旗比大家<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603536</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWAcwtf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWAcwtf.png&h=d632f9e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhfjVUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhfjVUZ.jpg&h=9ca494db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8p461M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8p461M.jpg&h=d0206053&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bcab006001e993947814ce693c5304daef3d1ca","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"其實我覺啲畜龍衝岀黎 前線就跑走主要原因係冇實體防線<br />\n<br />\n前係係人見到一咁多狗衝體黎都係驚係正常心理反應<br />\n<br />\n如果有返啲實在啲嘅野俾佢地揸住eg 鐵馬 水馬 <br />\n<br />\n應該可以hold得住"},{"pid":"273106387e9a6a92d9160d8c7cee33ea8f9fffdb","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺啲畜龍衝岀黎 前線就跑走主要原因係冇實體防線<br />\n<br />\n前線都係人一見到咁多狗衝過黎驚係正常心理反應<br />\n<br />\n如果有返啲實在啲嘅野俾佢地揸住eg 鐵馬 水馬 <br />\n<br />\n應該可以hold得住</blockquote>"},{"pid":"89d4c97546cd2c18ca9b2873f556d0ce6df70251","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f09cc3018233d5dc7871d6d7833802cff27b62cb","tid":1603530,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoFPyJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoFPyJu.jpg&h=15c1aa64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69613c27a266b2059362a58d9b035d4fa9ac8fe6","tid":1603530,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"就黎10/1 再係咁捱打唔得架<br />\n<br />\n快啲入黎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ec7068aafee7f2a2d9e3d34ba07f0d0f532ee6","tid":1603530,"uid":208262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-2